Meeting: April 6-10, 1997, Wellington Festival and Convention Centre, Wellington,
New Zealand. Plenary sessions will focus on updates for the practicing
clinician; combined sessions with the Australasian Society of Clinical
Immunology and Allergy and with the Australasian Sleep Association will
be offered as well. Abstract deadline is November 29, 1996. For information
contact the Thoracic Society of Australia and New Zealand, 1997 Annual
Scientific Meeting, c/o Conference Consultants and Management Limited,
PO Box 6175, Wellington, New Zealand. Phone: 64-4-472-7420; Fax: 64-4-472-7426.
