<P>Thomas L. Petty Aspen Lung Conference - 40th Annual Meeting: Biology
and Pathobiology of the Lung Circulation: June 4-7, 1997, Aspen Colorado.
The Conference will explore the normal functions of the lung vascular cells
and how they respond to shear stress, hypoxia, to inflammatory cells and
their mediators. Abstract deadline is February 3, 1997. For information
contact Norbert F. Voelkel, M.D., Box C272, University of Colorado Health
Sciences Center, 4200 E. 9th Avenue, Denver, CO 80262. Phone: 303-315-7767;
