<HEAD><TITLE>American Thoracic Society - Postgraduate Course on Clinical
Management and Control of Tuberculosis</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BACKGROUND="images/back.jpg">
<CENTER><IMG ALIGN="LEFT" SRC="images/smlogo.gif"><BR><H1>Postgraduate
Course on Clinical Management and Control of Tuberculosis</H1></CENTER>
<HR SIZE="5" NOSHADE="NOSHADE" WIDTH="100%"> 
<P><BR><BR>
</P>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER="2"><TR><TD COLSTART="1" ALIGN="CENTER" VALIGN="MIDDLE"><SMALL><A
HREF="oed.html#top">BACK TO MENU</A></SMALL></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<P></P>
<HR SIZE="5" WIDTH="70%">
<P></P>
<P><B>Postgraduate Course on Clinical Management and Control of Tuberculosis</B></P>
<H2>Held in: </H2>
<P>Denver, Colorado</P>
<H2>Presented by:</H2>
<P> National Jewish Center for Immunology and Respiratory Medicine, in
collaboration with Denver Health Department and University of Colorado School of
Medicine.</P>
<P>Early Registration Advised.</P>
<P>Applications Will Be Processed On A First-Come, First-Served Basis</P>
<H2>Dates:</H2>
<P>October 21-25, 1996</P>
<P>February 10-14, 1997</P>
<P>April 14-18, 1997</P>
<H2>Tuition:</H2>
<P>$560.00 physicians/nurses<BR>$280.00 fellows/residents</P>
