<H2>F2: ATS-ERS STATEMENT ON RESPIRATORY MUSCLES TESTING </H2></CENTER>
<HR SIZE="5" NOSHADE="NOSHADE" WIDTH="100%">
<P></P>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="2">
