<P><I>9:15</I> <B>Lung Transplantation</B>/M. Hertz, M.D., Minneapolis, MN</P>
<P><I>9:45</I> <B>Pulmonary Vascular Diseases and Thromboembolism</B>/S.
Idele, M.D., Ph.D., Tyler, TX</P>
<P>Discussion after each presentation/5 minutes</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
