<P><I>9:30</I> <B>Stress and Its Influence on Wheezing and Asthma Incidence
in a Cohort of Children of Atopic Parents</B>/D.R. Gold, M.D., M.P.H., Boston,
MA/R.J. Wright, M.D., Boston, MA</P>
