<UL>
  <LI><A HREF="http://www.etatne.ch/hapi/hapi.htm">Handicap - 
Internet</A>
</UL>
<H4>Italian</H4>
<UL>
  <LI><A HREF="http://www.agora.stm.it/enil4/">Italian E.N.I.L. 
Committee</A>
